+ Handle\nOut-of-Order Events
++ The Problem
+++_ Distributed systems delay events
+++_ Older update arrives after newer one
+++_ Risk: incorrect final state
++ AUTO CDC Solution
+++_ Compares sequence values on arrival
+++_ Higher sequence = more recent
+++_ Late-arriving older records ignored
-- No Manual Logic Needed
---_ No custom merge / timestamp checks
---_ No version comparison code
---_ Built-in to AUTO CDC API
-- Guarantee
---_ Destination always reflects correct state
---_ Idempotent processing
---_ Sequence column drives ordering
@endmindmap
